        <h2>
            现代世界体系（第三卷）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4532605">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4532605/" class="title-link">感悟</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4532605"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48143111/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48143111/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">区域的水</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-17"
      class="main-meta">2010-12-17 16:40:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4532605_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  世界现代体系是西方学者沃勒斯坦的著作，它从一个新的或多个视角解读西方资本主义的进程。当然，对书中的知识内容我是无法参透的，因为自身知识容量的限制以及其他方面的原因。虽然很难看懂，但是理解后你会以一个新的视角看世界。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4532605/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4532605_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4532605_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





